main event: A civilian reported seeing an unidentified object in Covington, Kentucky on July 5, 1966.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 15 seconds, The object was reported to be a single unidentified flying object, The observer has experience seeing objects for 8 years, The object was reported after contacting the U.S. Weather Bureau, No photographs or physical evidence were present in the report.
witness description: The witness is a 17-year-old male who has been observing objects for 8 years.
